text: Jérôme de Mayer was an archer from Belgium. Mayer competed at the 1920 Summer Olympics.Jérome DE MAYER He was born on 21 July 1875 and died on 18 August 1958.Jérôme De Mayer == References == Category:1875 births Category:1958 deaths Category:Belgian archers Category:Olympians for Belgium
